<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; text-align: center;">

<table style="width: 100%; border-spacing: 0; border-collapse: collapse; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">

            <table style="width: 600px; border-spacing: 0; border-collapse: collapse; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">

                <!-- Header 이미지 -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: center; padding: 10px">
                        <img src="https://hada-mail.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/%EB%89%B4+%EB%B0%B0%EB%84%88.jpg" alt="우리의 이야기를 하다" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; display: block;" />
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- 본문 내용 -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px;">💌</p>
                        <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 16px;">[{{title}}] - {{nickname}}님의 이야기</h2>
                        <p style="line-height: 1.8; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0; font-size: 14px">{{content}}</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- Footer -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color: rgba(81,159,241,0.1); text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">하다를 이용해주셔서 감사해요</p>
                        <p style="margin: 4px 0 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">하다가 당신의 이야기로 따뜻한 세상을 만들어 갑니다.</p>
                        <a href="https://hada.ganadacorp.com" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block;">
                            <img src="https://hada-mail.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/%ED%95%98%EB%8B%A4+%EB%A1%9C%EA%B3%A0.png" alt="하다 버튼" style="display: inline-block; width: 100px; height: auto; border: 0;" />
                        </a>
                    </td>
                </tr>

            </table>

        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
